Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.26,0:00:14.59,Default,,0,0,0,,We're getting really popular, you said?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.97,0:00:16.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought our merch was really cute...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.89,0:00:19.72,Default,,0,0,0,,It's because you had to go and\Npick such a weirdass name for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.10,0:00:21.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.56,0:00:24.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}TogeToge wristbands!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.89,0:00:26.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Anyone want a TogeToge towel?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.11,0:00:31.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I still think it's better than Shin-Kawasaki though...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.65,0:00:32.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.78,0:00:35.99,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll survive, at least\Nsomething's still really popular.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.61,0:00:37.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, let's do this!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.32,0:00:39.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Gimme a hug!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.91,0:00:43.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I am never showering again after this!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.66,0:00:45.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Your brain needs a shower! Sheesh...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.00,0:00:46.79,Default,,0,0,0,,You're right...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.13,0:00:48.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Not my type of thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.30,0:00:50.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.42,0:00:56.05,Default,,0,0,0,,If you have a moment, allow me to introduce myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.22,0:00:59.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}MIURA SHIOMI\NGOLDEN ARCHER CO.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.89,0:00:59.05,Default,,0,0,0,,..."Golden Archer"?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.68,0:01:02.43,Default,,0,0,0,,- Yes.\N- Why does that ring a bell?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.35,0:01:05.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! The talent agency!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.98,0:01:09.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Indeed!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.66,0:02:45.37,Default,,0,0,0,,10: WANDERVOGEL
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.07,0:02:42.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}So you are scouting us?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.99,0:02:45.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Yes, that is exactly why I reached out.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.33,0:02:46.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.45,0:02:51.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Please feel free to look us up online,\Nwe are a well established agency.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.38,0:02:54.42,Default,,0,0,0,,- How exactly?\N- They're pretty famous.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.59,0:02:57.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Many girls at my school\Nwant to get scouted by them.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.46,0:02:59.26,Default,,0,0,0,,And they also act as a label for bands.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.42,0:03:01.76,Default,,0,0,0,,But if they operate in showbiz, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.09,0:03:05.14,Default,,0,0,0,,The truth is, I love Diamond Dust!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.51,0:03:09.52,Default,,0,0,0,,But I cannot say the same of what\NDiamond Dust has become nowadays!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.68,0:03:13.02,Default,,0,0,0,,They've become so generic that\Nthey lost what made them so unique!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.36,0:03:15.52,Default,,0,0,0,,The one I loved was you, Momoka-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.69,0:03:18.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted to see you making music\Nthat you truly desired to create!!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.49,0:03:21.36,Default,,0,0,0,,And that's exactly what this band is!!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.53,0:03:22.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I know, right!!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.37,0:03:24.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Sit down.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.91,0:03:25.41,Default,,0,0,0,,...S-sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.49,0:03:28.70,Default,,0,0,0,,When DD managed to strike a major hit,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.87,0:03:31.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I came to the realization that my type of music
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.87,0:03:33.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't made for modern popular tastes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.38,0:03:35.09,Default,,0,0,0,,That's true...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.59,0:03:37.88,Default,,0,0,0,,And I don't think that's just me being pessimistic.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.55,0:03:42.30,Default,,0,0,0,,If anything, DD has gotten\Nmany fans by going down this path.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.47,0:03:47.18,Default,,0,0,0,,But in spite of that, these four\Nstill want to compete with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.60,0:03:50.43,Default,,0,0,0,,They want to prove my music\Ncan go toe to toe with theirs.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.06,0:03:53.44,Default,,0,0,0,,To the point they convinced me to give it a shot.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.81,0:03:55.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.73,0:03:57.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Momoka-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.86,0:03:58.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.40,0:03:59.94,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.61,0:04:02.86,Default,,0,0,0,,You will be at the\Nupcoming festival, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.95,0:04:06.45,Default,,0,0,0,,We need to "leave an\Nimpression" at the festival...?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.62,0:04:13.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an7}MIURA SHIOMI\NGOLDEN ARCHER CO.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.87,0:04:08.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Basically, if make enough of an impact,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.04,0:04:11.58,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll be easier for companies and labels to notice us.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.04,0:04:16.88,Default,,0,0,0,,And if we can bring in a lot of fans, then we can\Nprove to them that our music doesn't need to change.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.75,0:04:21.63,Default,,0,0,0,,So this festival is more like a big audition, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.22,0:04:23.84,Default,,0,0,0,,- Nina.\N- Y-yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.01,0:04:27.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you mind writing the lyrics for our next song?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.39,0:04:28.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.10,0:04:34.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to see what a song\Ninspired by my music is like.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.44,0:04:36.02,Default,,0,0,0,,OK!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.48,0:04:38.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not so sure about this one, chief.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.69,0:04:41.57,Default,,0,0,0,,- What are you even thinking?\N- I am down for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.03,0:04:43.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Those two really seem to understand each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.12,0:04:48.78,Default,,0,0,0,,How are the lyrics coming along?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.16,0:04:50.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Zero progress.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.24,0:04:53.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't you say there was\Nsomething you had in mind?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.00,0:04:55.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I did...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.37,0:04:57.25,Default,,0,0,0,,So where's the issue?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.50,0:04:58.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You wouldn't get it...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.25,0:05:02.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Putting feelings into words\Nmeans bringing them out.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.01,0:05:04.59,Default,,0,0,0,,So if I bring them out,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.76,0:05:08.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Then that means all of the repressed\Nmonsters within me will come flowing out...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.01,0:05:10.97,Default,,0,0,0,,What, you think you're too good for this?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.14,0:05:13.93,Default,,0,0,0,,You know how many songs I've had to make myself?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.10,0:05:15.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Ow ow ow ow!!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.52,0:05:18.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I can relate to not\Nwanting to share your pain...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.73,0:05:20.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, it's your shift.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.69,0:05:22.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Already...?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.91,0:05:27.57,Default,,0,0,0,,What now?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.11,0:05:28.95,Default,,0,0,0,,It's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.37,0:05:34.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morn-NAAAH
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.04,0:05:38.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.09,0:05:41.71,Default,,0,0,0,,How...?! Why?!!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.25,0:05:44.05,Default,,0,0,0,,What are y--
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.76,0:05:46.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.30,0:05:48.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.22,0:05:52.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I believe a certain Iseri works here part-time...?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.68,0:05:57.14,Default,,0,0,0,,She doesn't have any shifts today I'm afraid.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.27,0:06:03.07,Default,,0,0,0,,- Is that so...\N- Are you looking for her?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.48,0:06:06.36,Default,,0,0,0,,You must be Rupa-san, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.28,0:06:10.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}- SUBARU-CHAN!\N- What\N- MY MOM'S HERE! >:(\N- What did you expect ._.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.57,0:06:12.33,Default,,0,0,0,,They could've told me beforehand!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.08,0:06:17.62,Default,,0,0,0,,D-dad?? AH!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.50,0:06:23.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Nina?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.30,0:06:26.13,Default,,0,0,0,,And that's why you came running here?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.22,0:06:29.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Aaah... I feel so at peace here...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.47,0:06:32.64,Default,,0,0,0,,You still don't know why they came though, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.89,0:06:34.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Shouldn't you try talking to them?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.60,0:06:36.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you listening?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.15,0:06:41.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Nina...?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.15,0:06:44.23,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no point talking to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.40,0:06:47.99,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the same with your grandma, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.32,0:06:50.53,Default,,0,0,0,,They refuse to accept that we don't see eye to eye.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.70,0:06:53.03,Default,,0,0,0,,And treat you as if you were just sounding delirious.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.62,0:06:54.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Even then though...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.16,0:06:58.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides, I need to focus on the lyrics.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.25,0:07:00.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't waste my time before the festival on this.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.71,0:07:05.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone's future depends on it. I don't\Nhave the energy for anything else right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.67,0:07:08.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Sounds to me like you're just running away though.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.51,0:07:13.18,Default,,0,0,0,,So, are you sleeping here tonight?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.10,0:07:31.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an7}THE NEXT DAY
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.14,0:07:20.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hello?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.98,0:07:22.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Please don't contact me again.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.65,0:07:24.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You're the one who ran away.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.86,0:07:26.52,Default,,0,0,0,,This isn't what I meant by it though...!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.69,0:07:31.15,Default,,0,0,0,,They called me asking,\Nwhat was I supposed to do, lie?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.99,0:07:38.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1}To: ISERI MUNEO\NFrom: ISERI NINA{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.11,0:07:33.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You told them everything?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.45,0:07:35.95,Default,,0,0,0,,After you wrote them that letter,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.45,0:07:38.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Who wouldn't come after you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.25,0:07:40.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But why...?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.50,0:07:42.71,Default,,0,0,0,,You thought they'd just ignore it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.29,0:07:47.17,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're hurting, then stop\Nrunning away and just spit it out!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.26,0:07:51.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Nina?\NShe hung up...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.39,0:07:59.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.81,0:08:01.77,Default,,0,0,0,,They changed the lock??
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.19,0:08:04.85,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'm the tenant here!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.40,0:08:07.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Please provide me a new pair of keys!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.53,0:08:13.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Screw my parents, screw the company, screw everyone!!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.45,0:08:14.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up!!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.49,0:08:15.24,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.95,0:08:16.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.95,0:08:21.25,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll cover for you for a few days,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.04,0:08:24.29,Default,,0,0,0,,So have this as a present from Tomo-chan and I.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.67,0:08:29.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}TOKYO -> KUMAMOTO
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.75,0:08:28.67,Default,,0,0,0,,But why...?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.51,0:08:32.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You may have heard from Tomo-chan, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.59,0:08:36.51,Default,,0,0,0,,On a certain day,\NI was thinking of calling my mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.05,0:08:39.60,Default,,0,0,0,,However since my work\Nwas running until late,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.27,0:08:44.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought I might as well just call her tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.60,0:08:46.90,Default,,0,0,0,,My mom died that day.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.57,0:08:52.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Life offers less time and opportunities\Nthan we'd like to think.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.32,0:08:56.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Guess I should "cut it out with the monologues", heh.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.82,0:08:59.83,Default,,0,0,0,,You really think they care that much?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.33,0:09:02.54,Default,,0,0,0,,After they neglected me for so long.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.12,0:09:06.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Spare me the sound effects.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.25,0:09:08.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Heh, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.42,0:09:10.30,Default,,0,0,0,,So this is {\i1}your{\i0} weakness then?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.71,0:09:12.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I have no weaknesses or anything though.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.30,0:09:15.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Then just go already!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.47,0:09:16.84,Default,,0,0,0,,You too?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.01,0:09:19.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I think you're blowing this out of proportion.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.64,0:09:24.06,Default,,0,0,0,,What's holding you back?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.43,0:09:26.69,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no exams or bullying this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.40,0:09:30.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it because you're scared\Nof not convincing your father?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.78,0:09:33.82,Default,,0,0,0,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.32,0:09:35.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Not true? Then go already.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.78,0:09:37.82,Default,,0,0,0,,It is true.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.49,0:09:42.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Then even more reason to go.\NI'm not letting you back here till you do.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.95,0:09:45.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.63,0:09:55.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Back home...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.13,0:09:59.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\i1}The train bound for Suizenji and Hikarinomori...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.14,0:10:05.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}TATSUTAGUCHI STATION
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.31,0:10:05.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's do this!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.27,0:10:08.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Three, two, one...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.95,0:10:20.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Ouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.99,0:10:22.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Goddammit...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.92,0:10:30.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Nina!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.92,0:10:36.13,Default,,0,0,0,,We were looking for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.97,0:10:39.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Girls Band Cry.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.18,0:10:42.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1}Family Precepts
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.30,0:10:42.01,Default,,0,0,0,,A band?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.06,0:10:46.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that a viable career path these days?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.73,0:10:47.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Seems so.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.27,0:10:51.40,Default,,0,0,0,,She's already been approached by a showbiz agency,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.98,0:10:54.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Meaning she can do this professionally.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.32,0:10:57.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, or so I've heard at least.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.15,0:11:00.16,Default,,0,0,0,,- She's heard right...\N- But still...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.49,0:11:02.37,Default,,0,0,0,,You left here to study on your own,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.66,0:11:05.87,Default,,0,0,0,,And instead you started this project all on your own without telling us?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.49,0:11:08.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I've had a glimpse of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.50,0:11:12.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you realize how much you've hurt your mother?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.79,0:11:18.05,Default,,0,0,0,,There you go again.\NMom has nothing to do with this.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.80,0:11:23.30,Default,,0,0,0,,When I left, didn't you say "let her be"?.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.76,0:11:26.81,Default,,0,0,0,,We agreed on the same thing. To let me be.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.22,0:11:27.97,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not true.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.56,0:11:30.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I said you should get into university.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.23,0:11:36.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you realize how much I let you selfishly have?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.15,0:11:40.32,Default,,0,0,0,,You wanted to quit school, so I let you\Nsubmit your resignation.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.20,0:11:43.66,Default,,0,0,0,,You wanted to go to Tokyo, so I helped you move.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.53,0:11:46.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop pretending already...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.79,0:11:48.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I did everything on my own!!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.12,0:11:51.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm the one who quit! I'm the one who left!!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.96,0:11:55.13,Default,,0,0,0,,You only got the apartment\Nthanks to your mother's connections.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.21,0:11:59.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Remind me, who signed as\Nyour guarantor so you could rent?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.01,0:12:04.22,Default,,0,0,0,,You are still a minor. Do you know what that means?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.84,0:12:08.35,Default,,0,0,0,,That you must live under the supervision of adults.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.77,0:12:11.98,Default,,0,0,0,,So I should just obey you blindly?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.73,0:12:15.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I should let myself get bullied\Nlike nothing's happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.61,0:12:17.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Nina...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.65,0:12:18.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew it was pointless.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.32,0:12:20.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I shouldn't have hoped
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.19,0:12:25.12,Default,,0,0,0,,that you would listen to me,\Nor try to understand. I really tried.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.37,0:12:27.62,Default,,0,0,0,,But in the end, it all leads to this.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.95,0:12:28.95,Default,,0,0,0,,It's useless.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.54,0:12:33.79,Default,,0,0,0,,When you leave tomorrow, come with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.92,0:12:38.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.05,0:12:41.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are we going?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.22,0:12:44.59,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll realize very soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.83,0:13:14.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not going.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.17,0:13:17.08,Default,,0,0,0,,You're taking me to school, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.29,0:13:18.79,Default,,0,0,0,,We're just here to talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.54,0:13:24.09,Default,,0,0,0,,You told me what you wanted to say.\NBut there's something I wish to say to someone too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.80,0:13:28.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry to have made you come\Nall the way here in this heat.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.84,0:13:29.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}APOLOGY LETTER TO: ISERI MUNEO/NINA
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.10,0:13:29.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Do not worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.81,0:13:32.31,Default,,0,0,0,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.77,0:13:35.81,Default,,0,0,0,,It must've been pretty hot for you as well, Nina-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.31,0:13:37.85,Default,,0,0,0,,- If you may.\N- Ah, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.15,0:13:42.69,Default,,0,0,0,,After further inspection, the student\Nresponsible admitted her actions,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.78,0:13:48.20,Default,,0,0,0,,The school would like to extend an apology\Nfor not acting to the standards expected of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.91,0:13:52.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that all? Will the school not take responsibility?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.66,0:13:54.70,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not our intent,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.95,0:13:58.21,Default,,0,0,0,,However, we can't exactly publicly\Nacknowledge bullying in our school...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.58,0:14:01.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand that you may\Nnot be able to publicly,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.80,0:14:04.71,Default,,0,0,0,,But I was at least expecting\Nthat when it came to the truth--
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.05,0:14:05.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.38,0:14:07.13,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.38,0:14:09.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you to stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.51,0:14:14.93,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't need to say that Nina.\NYou're the {\i1}victim{\i0} here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.39,0:14:20.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Momoka-san... what would you do
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.56,0:14:24.73,Default,,0,0,0,,If, hypothetically, Nina never\Nreturned from Kumamoto?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.61,0:14:26.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll do what I must.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.82,0:14:29.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Tomo-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.99,0:14:31.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you hurt?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.71,0:14:37.54,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll be alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.04,0:14:40.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's believe in her.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.71,0:14:42.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome home.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.84,0:14:43.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.63,0:14:45.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Will you be eating dinner?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.27,0:14:57.93,Default,,0,0,0,,You going back then?\N- Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.98,0:15:00.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You're serious about that band?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.52,0:15:02.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.15,0:15:05.69,Default,,0,0,0,,You love it that much?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.70,0:15:13.99,Default,,0,0,0,,That song...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.70,0:15:18.58,Default,,0,0,0,,...It gave me the push I needed.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.91,0:15:23.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Back when I was told to\Nplay it smart and just "deal with it",
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.09,0:15:28.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1}Apology Letter{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.42,0:15:28.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Even when it felt impossible\Nto deal with anything anymore,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.59,0:15:30.47,Default,,0,0,0,,It gave me a push forward.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.51,0:15:38.93,Default,,0,0,0,,It told me that I wasn't wrong.\NThat I didn't need to deal with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.81,0:15:44.27,Default,,0,0,0,,It told me to not worry about\Nthe future and just take the leap.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.98,0:15:47.69,Default,,0,0,0,,It felt as if I was freefalling.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.86,0:15:51.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I wasn't sure if I was soaring into the great sky or plummeting to my doom,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.70,0:15:54.12,Default,,0,0,0,,But that song made me fly.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.45,0:15:58.08,Default,,0,0,0,,So I have no more homeland I can step back on.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.87,0:15:59.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Back then,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.50,0:16:05.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I may as well have been trying to kill myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.38,0:16:13.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe in reality I have no wings,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.05,0:16:16.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe this feeling of flying is all in my head, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.26,0:16:21.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Right now, I love myself more than I ever have.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.73,0:16:25.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I can proudly say that\N{\i1}this{\i0} is who I really am.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.36,0:16:32.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I get it now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.15,0:16:35.32,Default,,0,0,0,,But can we have one last dinner, at least?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.62,0:16:40.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Here you go! Lotus root curry!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.16,0:16:42.21,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been a while, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.46,0:16:45.00,Default,,0,0,0,,- Are you sure?\N- Why...?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.42,0:16:48.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Why? I mean, the family precepts...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.55,0:16:50.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, don't sweat it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.26,0:16:54.88,Default,,0,0,0,,After you left, the mood got kinda weird back here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.68,0:17:00.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Your dad even started drinking alcohol even though he's a light drinker.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.14,0:17:02.64,Default,,0,0,0,,To the point of getting drunk.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.15,0:17:06.52,Default,,0,0,0,,"What should I do for her?"
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.77,0:17:08.61,Default,,0,0,0,,He kept saying that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.73,0:17:12.28,Default,,0,0,0,,He's worried about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.61,0:17:16.66,Default,,0,0,0,,He may be a renowned researcher, but that doesn't mean,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.82,0:17:19.41,Default,,0,0,0,,he can't be adviced to learn some new things.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.49,0:17:22.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides, the Shinkansen ticket you used,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.33,0:17:26.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Your mom was the one who gave it to your friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.46,0:17:28.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Bet you never realized.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.67,0:17:32.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You know... we still love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.01,0:17:37.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Even those parents of ours,\NI have no doubt they still love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.80,0:17:39.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Just don't forget that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.77,0:17:42.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks for the meal.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.27,0:17:46.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you. For coming back to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.40,0:17:49.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I love you too, Nina.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.69,0:17:53.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Was it always so spicy?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.24,0:17:57.66,Default,,0,0,0,,This curry is so spicy it's making me cry...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.24,0:18:01.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1}FAMILY PRECEPTS{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.12,0:18:11.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an9}{\i1}Nina Age 10{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.46,0:18:17.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This void feeling, this eternal feeling,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.05,0:18:23.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Of answers that lead to superficial clichés{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.77,0:18:29.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this that song you love so much?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.98,0:18:31.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.69,0:18:33.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.86,0:18:35.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you hate it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.49,0:18:37.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I bet you do after all that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.70,0:18:41.83,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a good song.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.04,0:18:46.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Quite good in fact.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.83,0:18:48.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.04,0:18:54.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry you had to deal with such a\Nselfish daughter who'd never listen to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.01,0:18:58.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Please stop smoking so much, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.93,0:19:10.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm leaving. I'm leaving!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.15,0:19:12.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm leaving for good!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.48,0:19:14.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Nina!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.15,0:19:17.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.65,0:19:19.20,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.45,0:19:22.74,Default,,0,0,0,,What more could you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.12,0:19:26.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Stay safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.75,0:19:31.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I will.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.29,0:19:33.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Nina!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.13,0:19:36.46,Default,,0,0,0,,The keys to your apartment!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.46,0:19:38.26,Default,,0,0,0,,New keys?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.59,0:19:42.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Why change them?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.89,0:19:43.93,Default,,0,0,0,,A gift from your dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.61,0:19:55.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.82,0:20:03.28,Default,,0,0,0,,When I finish this next song and\Nget to sing it, if it's okay with you...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.45,0:20:05.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Will you come listen to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.74,0:20:07.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I will.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.87,0:20:09.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.54,0:20:11.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Nina...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.67,0:20:16.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm leaving!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.67,0:20:19.13,Default,,0,0,0,,And thanks for cutting the branch!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.63,0:20:21.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Take care!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.14,0:20:28.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even if you were so intrusive and unbearable...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.81,0:20:30.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I still loved you.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.10,0:20:34.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Goodbye... no. See you again!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.06,0:20:38.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Thank you for traveling with us.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.57,0:20:40.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}To take the Chuo, Yamanote,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.32,0:20:45.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8} Keihin-Tohokku, Tokaido, Joban Lines... 
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.32,0:20:45.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"VOID AND CATHARSIS"
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.95,0:20:45.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss? Miss!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.82,0:20:46.62,Default,,0,0,0,,S-sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.08,0:20:48.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? It's you again!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.12,0:20:50.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Had a good nap?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.12,0:20:51.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.80,0:21:05.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm home!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.60,0:21:17.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Nina!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.57,0:21:24.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's the souvenirs?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.61,0:21:27.28,Default,,0,0,0,,No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.66,0:21:29.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you all here?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.66,0:21:34.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Momoka-san wanted to make sure\Nyou'd come back safe and sound.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.12,0:21:36.83,Default,,0,0,0,,If one more day went by,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.00,0:21:40.05,Default,,0,0,0,,She would've driven us all four to Kumamoto to get you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.05,0:21:43.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Even insisted she'd drive herself.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.72,0:21:47.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't want Rupa-san to take the spotlight, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.80,0:21:49.64,Default,,0,0,0,,You all agreed to it, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.14,0:21:51.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold up, why's she crying?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.68,0:21:53.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Was it that traumatizing?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.43,0:21:55.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm? I don't think she's actually crying.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.69,0:21:57.10,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you think, Rupa-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.52,0:21:59.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.15,0:22:03.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.33,0:22:12.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm home!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.75,0:22:15.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome home!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.87,0:22:17.04,Default,,0,0,0,,You got the lyrics done?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.50,0:22:20.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I got them! It's gonna be a good song!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.47,0:22:29.93,Default,,0,0,0,,  
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.55,0:22:34.93,Default,,0,0,0,,   
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.98,0:22:39.35,Default,,0,0,0,,   
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.08,0:23:46.09,Default,,0,0,0,,   
